Bridging the gap between "A New Hope" and "The Empire Strikes Back", this is the story of how the Empire dealt with the destruction of the Death Star and how Darth Vader discovered that he has a son. The voice talent is provided by members of Casting Call Club (https://castingcall.club). 

"Darth Vader #2"
